  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME AN ASTEROID MINER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/ea65513b0f4db0246d98a1f352bc0de5.poster.avif?t=1723214283\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/ea65513b0f4db0246d98a1f352bc0de5.webm?t=1723214283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Loot the precious gems contained within the asteroids and use them to upgrade your spaceship from the most basic vessel into a steamrolling death machine!<br><br><strong></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SINGLEPLAYER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/1c36fa6d18e2407c144f28e9c6a90356.poster.avif?t=1723214283\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/1c36fa6d18e2407c144f28e9c6a90356.webm?t=1723214283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Stand your ground against waves of vicious alien ships. Fight through galaxies of increasing difficulty and ultimately challenge the boss alien.<br><br>As your ship grows stronger from looting, for each level-up you'll be provided a choice of various upgrades to select. Take a moment to think about how you'll build your ship as all upgrades unlock interesting and valuable abilities!<br><br><strong></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/dc82fb4aa5c8372c418755138b975240.poster.avif?t=1723214283\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/dc82fb4aa5c8372c418755138b975240.webm?t=1723214283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Instead of aliens you will fight against other miners in PvP multiplayer matches of up to 16 contestants.<br><br>Allocate your loot in real time into upgrade levels to make your ship perform the way it needs to to come out on top!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME AN ASTEROID MINER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/ea65513b0f4db0246d98a1f352bc0de5.poster.avif?t=1723214283\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/ea65513b0f4db0246d98a1f352bc0de5.webm?t=1723214283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Loot the precious gems contained within the asteroids and use them to upgrade your spaceship from the most basic vessel into a steamrolling death machine!<br><br><strong></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SINGLEPLAYER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/1c36fa6d18e2407c144f28e9c6a90356.poster.avif?t=1723214283\" width=616 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/1c36fa6d18e2407c144f28e9c6a90356.webm?t=1723214283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Stand your ground against waves of vicious alien ships. Fight through galaxies of increasing difficulty and ultimately challenge the boss alien.<br><br>As your ship grows stronger from looting, for each level-up you'll be provided a choice of various upgrades to select. Take a moment to think about how you'll build your ship as all upgrades unlock interesting and valuable abilities!<br><br><strong></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912100/extras/dc82fb4aa5c8372c418755138b9